BiqhTableMaps.SqlQuery:
SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.SegmentType AS [ProviderKey]
	, b_ct.Id AS [ClassificationTypeId]
	, oe.SegmentType AS [Name]
FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
	INNER JOIN dbo.ClassificationType b_ct ON b_ct.ProviderKey = N'Segment' AND b_ct.ProviderId = @ProviderId
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT 
	N'Segment' AS [ProviderKey]
	, N'Segment' AS [Code]
	, N'Segment' AS [Name]

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey],
		oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [OwnProviderId],
       oe.CompanySymbol AS [Symbol]
FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	b_c.ProviderKey + '|' + b_cl.ProviderKey  AS [ProviderKey]
	, b_c.Id AS [CompanyId]
	, b_cl.Id AS [ClassificationId]

FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
	INNER JOIN dbo.Company b_c ON b_c.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_c.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Classification b_cl ON b_cl.ProviderKey = oe.SegmentType AND b_cl.ProviderId = @ProviderId
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT 
	N'Owner' AS [ProviderKey]
	, N'Owner' AS [Code]
	, N'Owner' AS [Name]

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey]
	, b_c.Id AS [CompanyId]
	, b_sr.Id AS [SustainabilityReportId]

FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
    INNER JOIN dbo.Company b_c ON b_c.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_c.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.SustainabilityReport b_sr ON b_sr.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_sr.ProviderId = @ProviderId

WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	 b_c.Id AS [CompanyId]
	, b_e.Id AS [EsgId]
FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
	INNER JOIN dbo.Company b_c ON b_c.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_c.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Esg b_e ON b_e.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_e.ProviderId = @ProviderId
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey],
oe.TotalGrade AS [TotalGrade],
oe.EnvironmentalGrade AS [EnvironmentalGrade],
oe.SocialGrade AS [SocialGrade],
oe.GovernanceGrade AS [GovernanceGrade],
oe.ApprovedDateTime AS [EndDateTime]
FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey]
    ,oe.LegalRisk AS [LegalRisk]
	,oe.LegalRiskNote AS [LegalRiskNote]
 	, es.Id AS [EnvironmentalSustainabilityId]
 	, ss.Id AS [SocialSustainabilityId]
     , gs.Id AS [GovernanceSustainabilityId]


FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe
    left join dbo.EnvironmentalSustainability es on es.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier and es.ProviderId = @ProviderId
    left join dbo.SocialSustainability ss on ss.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier and ss.ProviderId = @ProviderId
    left join dbo.GovernanceSustainability gs on gs.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier and gs.ProviderId = @ProviderId

WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.ObjectId AS [ProviderKey]
	, b_o.Id AS [ObjectId]
	, b_orc.Id AS [ObjectRiskCategoryId],
    oe.Tornado AS [Tornado],
oe.ExtratropicalStorm AS [ExtratropicalStorm],
oe.Hail AS [Hail],
oe.Lightning AS [Lightning],
oe.Wildfire AS [Wildfire],
oe.FlashFlood AS [FlashFlood],
oe.CoastalFlood AS [CoastalFlood],
oe.TropicalCycloneYear AS [TropicalCycloneYear],
oe.TropicalCyclone AS [TropicalCyclone],
oe.DroughtStressYear AS [DroughtStressYear],
oe.DroughtStress AS [DroughtStress],
oe.FireWeatherStressIndexYear AS [FireWeatherStressIndexYear],
oe.FireWeatherStressIndex AS [FireWeatherStressIndex],
oe.HeatStressYear AS [HeatStressYear],
oe.HeatStress AS [HeatStress],
oe.ColdStressYear AS [ColdStressYear],
oe.ColdStress AS [ColdStress],
oe.PrecipitationYear AS [PrecipitationYear],
oe.Precipitation AS [Precipitation],
oe.RiverFloodYear AS [RiverFloodYear],
oe.RiverFlood AS [RiverFlood],
oe.SeaLevelRiseYear AS [SeaLevelRiseYear],
oe.SeaLevelRise AS [SeaLevelRise]

FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
	INNER JOIN dbo.Object b_o ON b_o.ProviderKey = oe.ObjectId AND b_o.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.ObjectRiskCategory b_orc ON b_orc.ProviderKey = N'Physical' AND b_orc.ProviderId = @ProviderId
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT 
	N'Physical' AS [ProviderKey]
	, N'Physical' AS [Code]
	, N'Physical' AS [Name]

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.ObjectId AS [ProviderKey]
--	, b_ot.Id AS [ObjectTypeId]
    ,oe.ObjectId AS [OwnProviderId]
    , oe.Origin AS [Origin]
    , oe.Insurance AS [Insurance]
    , oe.InsuranceNote AS [InsuranceNote]



FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0
   -- and oe.ObjectId <> '990020_376' --same ObjectId has different ObjectName

SELECT DISTINCT
	 b_o.Id AS [ObjectId]
	, b_c.Id AS [CompanyId]
	, b_cr.Id AS [CompanyRoleId]
FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
	INNER JOIN dbo.Object b_o ON b_o.ProviderKey = oe.ObjectId AND b_o.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.Company b_c ON b_c.ProviderKey = oe.CompanyIdentifier AND b_c.ProviderId = @ProviderId
	INNER JOIN dbo.CompanyRole b_cr ON b_cr.ProviderKey = N'Owner' AND b_cr.ProviderId = @ProviderId
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey]
    ,oe.ClimateChangeExposureGrade AS [ClimateChangeExposureGrade]
	,oe.LowCarbonTransitionExposureGrade AS [LowCarbonTransitionExposureGrade]



FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey]
	,oe.GovernancePillarRisk AS [GovernancePillarRisk]
	,oe.GovernancePillarRiskNote AS [GovernancePillarRiskNote]



FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

SELECT DISTINCT
	oe.CompanyIdentifier AS [ProviderKey]
	,oe.SocialPillarRisk AS [SocialPillarRisk]
	,oe.SocialPillarRiskNote AS [SocialPillarRiskNote]



FROM
	@Schema.ObjectEsg oe 
WHERE
	oe.Record_ImportId = @ImportId
	AND oe.Record_HasError = 0

BiqhTableRowMapRowLinkSets.SqlQuery:
SELECT
	b_o.Id as [TableRowId],
	bb_o.Id as [Link]
FROM
	dbo.Object b_o
	inner join dbo.Object bb_o on bb_o.ProviderId = @BaseProviderId
	and b_o.[OwnProviderId] = bb_o.[OwnProviderId]
WHERE
	b_o.ProviderId = @ProviderId
